A state of alertness/alertness system
==============================
If we observe in the frame of energy/the behavior of energy/streaming of energy/nature/waves so on then alertness have no any meaning since waves/energy work on the principle
of affinity towards its stability. Energy don't have any task to do, it just proceed towards stability and what event get created due to their process become the task. Energy never
move blindly even they don't have eye like lives.
But when we observe in the frame of lives then the same alertness become valuable for smoothness of lives. Every lives have some senses/mind/observation/understanding..
on the basis of that they apply their alertness system instantly. Alertness system is just like a system who is responsible for decrease the unnatural/forceful/pressurize changes.

Alertness system
-----------------------
Every system makes by collections of small units of stuff here also the alertness system also get build by many small waves of different frequencies and when it realize any
sudden activity towards that system it automatically get alert. Based on the alert the system try to minimize the effect of unnatural changes that going to occur/diminish
the effect/change the path/restructure the alertness system for that moment to overcome the unnatural effect.

***Alertness system make one ready to accept the changes/refuse the changes/flexible for smoothness***

Alertness system is also a pooled structure of energy/waves system who protect the lives from unexpected/sudden changes, it is active by using our senses/mind/observation
/understanding/realization..so on.

Based on the intensity of senses/mind/observation..or energy within the lives it works, since it build on top of energy within only. You may observe not only the human but
also every lives have some what alertness system.

Ex-
-When you pickup a stone near a dog, you observe dog, the dog get alert and looking next activity of stone/your hand/body movement.It is not dog but the alertness system
within dog get alert and the same alertness system get reflected on the body language/eye language of dog.

-Some instance come suddenly towards you eye, your eye bro get automatically closed suddenly. It is not you/observation/mind/senses but some system/alertness who looking something
unexpected things comes towards eye. Yup but this system use the energy gather by mind/senses/observation.

-When you drive vehicle, you can observe it is not the human mind but the centralized attention derive the vehicle and alertness system are in almost active state and it suddenly wake up 
just before attention realize something going to be wrong suddenly.

In fact the spread attention get transformed into thin centralized alertness system when it require.

***Alertness system always make your life towards smooth streaming/natural streaming*** 